15 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP. There is hereby authorized, for the Department
16 of Commerce - State Bank Department for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the
17 following maximum number of part-time or temporary employees, to be known as
18 "Extra Help", payable from funds appropriated herein for such purposes: four
19 (4) temporary or part-time employees, when needed, at rates of pay not to
20 exceed those provided in the Uniform Classification and Compensation Act, or
21 its successor, or this act for the appropriate classification.
22
